Message.Jp: ＜ウィークリー＞長期魔物討伐：テル村

Message.En:
I have a request for all Arisen staying in Tel
long-term. Recently, <LQEM> 
have been increasing
around the village. While it's not urgent, I'd
like to ask you to defeat <LQVA> of them during
your stay here.
Message.Jp:
テルに長期滞在する覚者の諸君にお願いがある
最近村周辺に<LQEM>が増えていてな
急を要するわけではないが、ここにいる間に<LQVA>体ほど討伐を頼みたい
